divs: Sighting Detailswalking down the street observing the moon with a lot of clouds obscuring it. I first noticed the object because since childhood I have observed many objects in sky, including planets and stars. I hunted for the galaxy Andromeda at one time. Whenn I thought I saw a very interesting star formation I kept looking at it, noticing the very regular 5 star pattern that was made. Then I realized it was impossible to see the stars, as the sky was obscured by clouds. I stopped looking at the object because I had other things to do and this funny craft was not moving or doing anything..
Summary: five stars in a pentagle, I thought were stars but then observed heavy clouds so object was below clouds and structure was very regular
